label: Typhoid

label: Chicken pox

label: Impetigo

label: Dengue

label: Fungal infection

label: Common Cold

label: Dimorphic Hemorrhoids
text: For the past few weeks, I've been noticing a persistent discomfort in my anal region, often accompanied by itching and burning sensations, especially after long periods of sitting or during bowel movements. label: Arthritis

label: Acne
